175 A.3d 161 STATE OF NEW JERSEY, PLAINTIFF-RESPONDENT, v. DANILO I. LEONEN, DEFENDANT-PETITIONER.

C-258 September Term 2017

079903 October 26, 2017

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-004764-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
